  "description": "<i>Tetriz</i> (not to be confused with <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Tetriz\">the other games by the same name</a>) is a <i><a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Tetris\">Tetris</a></i> clone running either in a window on the Workbench or on its own screen. It is level-based, so clearing a certain number of lines resets the playfield and raises the difficulty. Higher levels are not only faster, but introduce blocking bricks and super-fast bricks. It is a well-featured implementation, with various bonuses for high drops, multiple lines, completing lines of one single colour or clearing the entire playfield. ",
